description: Very easy and light banana bread.
keywords: Banana bread,Pescatarian,Halal,Seafood free,Soy free,Vegetarian,Tree nut free,Sesame free,Peanut free
name: Chocolate Chip Banana Bread Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 170* fan forced, 150* no fan.
In a bowl put the bananas and using a fork mash it up. Add milk, butter, eggs, vanilla and sugar till combined.
Add all dry ingredients and mix till all combined. Decorate with a half sliced banana lengthways.

Spoon into a pre lined loaf tin and bake for 35 mins without opening the door then do a prick test to see if it's cooked if not put for another 10 mins. (If you find the top is browning to fast put a piece of foil loosely quickly over the top) When done rest in loaf tin for 5 mins then transfer to a cooling rack till it's cool then remove and cut and eat.
Store in airtight container for 3 days for in the freezer for 3 months individually wrapped.
